Texts.Chs: 从现在开始，来尝试繁殖出最棒的蜜蜂吧！我相信你一定能做到的。
Texts.Eng: From here on out, it's up to you to experiment and breed the best bees you can! Bee all you can bee!

Texts.Chs: 为了能充分地利用好你的蜂园，并且加快蜂蜜的产出，我建议你制造一个^orange;蜂蜜灌装机^reset;，它会更好地帮助你把蜂蜜进行灌装。你或许还会需要一些瓶子或者罐子。
Texts.Eng: To make the most out of your bee farm, you'll want to harvest honey. Try to build a ^orange;Honey Jarrer^reset; to aid with this process. Toss in some honey jars while you're at it.
